beIN SPORTS 8.desc_ar: This will be just the third season in which Atlético Madrid have faced a Norwegian side in major European competition, after 1991-92 v Fyllingen in the Cup Winners’ Cup  and 2010-11 v Rosenborg in the UEFA Europa League.
